{"tid":1098872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"闖入侵侵渡假屋中國籍女人 身上有四部電話、惡意軟件手我指及偵測cctv儀器 事發兩日前由上海飛去美國","createTime":"2019-04-09T11:30:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-11T05:21:41.000Z","uid":48083,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d722af5abbb7a0fdc34ccd7eeabbea37557ee1ad","tid":1098872,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:30:22.000Z","msg":"Yujing Zhang was arrested at Mar-a-Lago late last month <br />\nProsecutors reveal they found thousands in cash in her hotel room<br />\nThey also found a signal detector to seek hidden cameras<br />\nHer lawyer says she paid $20,000 to an organizer to be there <br />\nShe was arrested with four cell phones on her at the club <br />\nAlso a thumb drive with malicious malware <br />\nSecret Service agent inserted the thumb drive into his computer<br />\nTrump was golfing at the time of the arrest and wasn't there <br />\nPresident Trump called the arrest a 'fluke' and praised the receptionist <br />\nFederal prosecutor says she 'lies to everyone she encounters<br />\n<br />\n⋯⋯Prosecutors revealed the results of a search on the hotel room that she had booked. <span style=\"color: red;\">In addition to the signal detector, authorities located another cell phone &ndash; bringing the total she had with her on the trip to five &ndash; plus a total of nine USB drives and five SIM cards, according to prosecutors. ..</span>.<br />\n<br />\nA day after her arrival in the U.S., Zhang checked into the $400-a-night Colony Hotel about two miles north of Mar-a-Lago.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">There, Garcia said, investigators found numerous electronic devices a</span>nd $7,620 as well as about $600 in Chinese Yuan.<br />\n<br />\nAccording to court documents, Zhang told a Secret Service agent before her arrest that her contact Charles 'told her to travel from Shanghai, China, to Palm Beach, Florida, to attend this event and attempt to speak with a member of the President&rsquo;s family about Chinese and American foreign economic relations.' <br />\n<br />\nThe FBI has been investigating the incident for possible espionage connections. <span style=\"color: red;\">The timing of her arrival in the U.S. also reveals she came her just two days before her bust inside the president's club on a Saturday.</span><br />\n<br />\nShe flew from Shanghai to Newark, arriving March 28. The was arrested March 30. <br />\n<br />\nTrump was golfing at the time of the arrest and wasn't there.   <br />\n<br />\nZhang is charged with entering a restricted area and lying to a federal agent. The magistrate judge overseeing the case revoked her visa, according to the Palm Beach Daily News.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6900251/Chinese-woman-arrested-Mar-Lago-signal-detector-hidden-cameras.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dailymail.co.uk%2Fnews%2Farticle-6900251%2FChinese-woman-arrested-Mar-Lago-signal-detector-hidden-cameras.html&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLWjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=be7feceb\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-6900251/Chinese-woman-arrested-Mar-Lago-signal-detector-hidden-cameras.html</a>"},{"pid":"560e8209a8202926cccdb2e2d44355ac2bed4c0e","tid":1098872,"uid":15205,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:40:29.000Z","msg":"做特務都做得柒過人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33823f4764b395e02cb1e75a36faa6e93ee3d8ef","tid":1098872,"uid":126283,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:44:29.000Z","msg":"斷正即啪啦<br />\n敵對行為黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"828e4216dce7fcd44c79bbf0c75f190cb01dc269","tid":1098872,"uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:48:28.000Z","msg":"更正<br />\n嗰偵測ccTv儀器係喺酒店揾到<br />\n中文：<br />\n<br />\n中國女子擅闖特朗普莊園　房間搜出反監控裝置<br />\n<br />\n立場報道2019/4/9 &mdash; 15:57<br />\n海湖莊園<br />\n中國女子 Yujing Zhang（音譯張玉靜）上月 30 日闖入美國總統特朗普位於佛羅里達的海湖莊園，被控向聯邦探員說謊及非法闖入，美國時間星期一出席保釋聆訊，控方在她的酒店房搵出一個可以偵測隱藏鏡頭的反監控裝置、大量電訊設備和 8,000 元美金，約 62,400 港元，控方認為她有潛逃風險建議拒絕她保釋，保釋聆訊下星期一再續，張玉靜要繼續還押。<br />\n<br />\n張玉靜星期一在西棕櫚灘法庭出席保釋聆訊，控方透露在她的酒店房搜到一個偵測隱藏鏡頭訊號的裝置，9 隻 USB，5 張電話卡和一部電話，還有 8,000 美元現金和幾張信用卡。檢察官在聆訊中稱張玉靜「對遇到的每個人都說謊」，至於她是否間諜，聯邦調查局仍在調查，目前未有起訴她任何涉及間諜的罪行。而張玉靜在美國無任何聯繫，控方擔心她有潛逃風險，她要還押等候下星期一保釋聆訊續審。<br />\n<br />\n32 歲的張玉靜是在 3 月 30 日，闖入海湖莊園，聲稱到莊園游泳，之後又稱是出席華裔社團活動，後來被職員揭發被捕，當時她身上攜帶裝有電腦病毒的 USB。美國國務卿蓬佩奧早前認為，事件反映中國的威脅。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/中國女子擅闖特朗普莊園-房間搜出反監控裝置/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%93%85%E9%97%96%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E8%8E%8A%E5%9C%92-%E6%88%BF%E9%96%93%E6%90%9C%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%8D%E7%9B%A3%E6%8E%A7%E8%A3%9D%E7%BD%AE%2F&d=Srnh2QCYUB68P60bIi3tLWjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=90ea61b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E6%93%85%E9%97%96%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E8%8E%8A%E5%9C%92-%E6%88%BF%E9%96%93%E6%90%9C%E5%87%BA%E5%8F%8D%E7%9B%A3%E6%8E%A7%E8%A3%9D%E7%BD%AE%2F&h=579c85bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/中國女子擅闖特朗普莊園-房間搜出反監控裝置/</a>"},{"pid":"52412f5d17885203430688eccf1a70a74a65edc8","tid":1098872,"uid":35430,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:49:20.000Z","msg":"斬手斬腳掟落海餵鯊魚啦死共狗"},{"pid":"5cb040eca783403e712c3d3067dbd6fe83206ba8","tid":1098872,"uid":82640,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"52412f5d17885203430688eccf1a70a74a65edc8","tid":1098872,"uid":35430,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:49:20.000Z","msg":"斬手斬腳掟落海餵鯊魚啦死共狗"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:50:31.000Z","msg":"拎去做慰安婦啦"},{